%% ============================================================
%% Assignment 2 – Agent turn automaton
%% ============================================================
%% Models which actions can be taken when within a single turn.
%% One turn = one player's turn (human or agent).
%%
%% ACTION SPACE (what can be taken when):
%%   AwaitRoll    : ROLL only (human types "Roll"; agent auto-rolls)
%%   RobberDiscard: (automatic) each player with >7 cards discards half
%%   RobberPlace  : (automatic) robber placed on random tile
%%   RobberSteal  : (automatic) one qualifying player gives card to roller
%%   PostRoll     : (automatic) distribute resources; then → BuildOrTrade
%%   BuildOrTrade : BUILD (settlement | city | road), TRADE, LIST; repeat or pass
%%   AwaitGo      : GO only (blocks until "go" for step-forward R2.4)
%% ============================================================

stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR

    [*] --> AwaitRoll : turn starts

    AwaitRoll --> RollDice : ROLL (human) or auto (agent)

    RollDice --> PostRoll : dice ≠ 7
    RollDice --> RobberDiscard : dice = 7

    RobberDiscard --> RobberPlace : all with >7 cards have discarded
    note right of RobberDiscard : Players with >7 cards discard half (round down)

    RobberPlace --> RobberSteal : robber placed on new tile
    note right of RobberPlace : Robber on random tile (R2.5)

    RobberSteal --> PostRoll : one qualifying player gives random card to roller
    note right of RobberSteal : Qualifying = settlement/city adjacent to robber tile

    PostRoll --> BuildOrTrade : resources distributed (if any)
    note right of PostRoll : Tiles with dice number produce; robber blocks tile

    BuildOrTrade --> BuildOrTrade : BUILD (settlement/city/road) or TRADE
    BuildOrTrade --> AwaitGo : no more actions / LIST only / pass

    AwaitGo --> [*] : GO (R2.4 step-forward)
    note right of AwaitGo : Blocks until "go" received; then next player's turn

    %% Allow multiple builds/trades in same turn
    BuildOrTrade --> BuildOrTrade : build again
    BuildOrTrade --> BuildOrTrade : trade again
